import React from "react";

const Faq = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <FaqContainer id="faq">
        <FaqH1>Întrebări frecvente</FaqH1>
        <FaqWrapper>
          <FaqCard>
            <FaqIcon src={Icon1} />
            <FaqH2>Card1</FaqH2>
            <FaqP>Random text for each card</FaqP>
          </FaqCard>
          <FaqCard>
            <FaqIcon src={Icon2} />
            <FaqH2>Card2</FaqH2>
            <FaqP>Random text for each card</FaqP>
          </FaqCard>
          <FaqCard>
            <FaqIcon src={Icon3} />
            <FaqH2>Card3</FaqH2>
            <FaqP>Random text for each card</FaqP>
          </FaqCard>
        </FaqWrapper>
      </FaqContainer>
    </>
  );
};

export default Faq;
